sections.text:
55-101.Military code; how cited.

Sections 55-101 to 55-181 shall be known and may be cited as the Military Code.

SourceLaws 1929, c. 189, § 1, p. 657;C.S.1929, § 55-105;R.S.1943, § 55-101;Laws 1961, c. 272, § 1, p. 806;Laws 1969, c. 459, § 1, p. 1581;Laws 1971, LB 19, § 1;Laws 1991, LB 313, § 1;Laws 2003, LB 69, § 2;Laws 2010, LB550, § 1.
